Get 45% off the Magic Mind bundle with with my link: [https://magicmind.com/CBOOKJAN](https://magicmind.com/CBOOKJAN)  In this week's episode of the Major Issues Podcast, the hosts dive headfirst into the multiversal madness that is Marvel's What If...? Season 3—the final chapter of the animated anthology that's been flipping the MCU on its head since Day One.  Was it a satisfying conclusion or just another trip to the variant junkyard? Did Jeffrey Wright’s Watcher finally hit his breaking point with all the chaos? And most importantly, can Marvel out-weird itself after this? Grab your favorite Infinity Snack and tune in for all the laughs, tangents, and hot takes you’ve come to expect. This episode is so wild, even Kang would take notes!

